{"tid":1944750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Nemo me impune lacessit","createTime":"2020-03-26T15:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T14:00:27.000Z","uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8e92a67c400ce1933ed4840161844121d01391","tid":1944750,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「人不犯我 我不犯人」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">你若犯我 十倍奉還</div>"},{"pid":"6a5773405cbb43f623b2a8340376e8b6249079db","tid":1944750,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 人生為己，天經地義，<br />\n人不為己，天誅地滅。</div>"},{"pid":"1422edfd6e039b7cf71763c5a75c0de9f6511d28","tid":1944750,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a5773405cbb43f623b2a8340376e8b6249079db","tid":1944750,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 人生為己，天經地義，<br />\n人不為己，天誅地滅。</div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:10:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">然而不信佛的，所以不為己，當天誅地滅</div>"},{"pid":"b2fdcc2819c92fdb7ab7aa855db3de49d0d5c7f1","tid":1944750,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">若你種下惡的種子，我為你開出惡的果</div>"},{"pid":"b68265bea1e4dcac702c7031563fdf13a8200301","tid":1944750,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">孤兒勝在 一無所有<br />\n無所擁有 無所畏懼</div>"},{"pid":"a23c342a1487439e2eded2249977dc4a080cc9d9","tid":1944750,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T01:00:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">誰在用虛情假意換取憐憫</div>"},{"pid":"8700b5744d1a4e0c4865b5ed2a35dc1efd3fdf46","tid":1944750,"uid":271864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot